text: Rob Ehrens (born 30 October 1957) is a Dutch equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1988 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1957 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1988 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Limburg (Netherlands)
